author: julianfoad
msg: Fix a pool usage bug in the svn_rangelist_inheritable2() and consequently
svn_mergeinfo_inheritable2() APIs. The result was not completely allocated
As far as I can tell the current trunk Subversion code does not rely on the
output being allocated in the result pool. I found this by code inspection.
This bug was introduced in r866302.
Note also that this bug was hiding a bug in the previous line which I fixed
a few minutes ago in r1569731.
